00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.500
Fazaila: Today
is Eid,

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.889
its more interesting in Pakistan because

00:00:13.889 --> 00:00:19.960
normally your relatives are living right next
to each other and you get to see everyone

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:28.960
every single day but here you only see each
other once in a while because of work, college, and everything.

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:35.400
One of the points of Eid is
to wear new clothes, new shoes, its more exciting

00:00:38.550 --> 00:00:46.550
with new clothes 
