but again only for a short while

00:00:53.190 --> 00:00:58.800
I'm not saying she doesn't wear it at all but most of the
time she is in English clothes.

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:04.510
I told you to get dressed in Shalwaar
Kameez and you still come down in this

00:01:04.510 --> 00:01:09.159
-It doesn't matter
-Of course it does. We're going to Green Street.

