Nan: Its dark now. Nobody is going to see her.

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:15.439
-Nan is with me on this. I don't care.

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:20.530
I like music, and I like rapping and I like

00:01:20.530 --> 00:01:27.530
writing my own lyrics because writing my own
lyrics I get to express how I feel
0:01:28.759,0:01:33.460
because sometimes you don't want to tell anyone else
what you really think and how you feel
0:01:33.460,0:01:37.110
and you just want to word it like poetry or something
like that.

