00:02:41.970 --> 00:02:45.094
A total embarrassment what she is wearing.
Our own traditional clothes are so nice. 

00:02:44.379 --> 00:02:51.379
I told her so often to wear them,
but she still comes out dressed like this. 

00:02:54.890 --> 00:03:01.780
